{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5d431ea32d","title":"和周恩来应对联","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0b206fe3c8","index":0,"year":1956,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"5d431ea32d"}],"tags":[{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji37","name":"毛泽东全集第37卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/37-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji37":{"comments":[{"id":"7ace84c88d","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"5d431ea32d","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"年，毛泽东和周恩来一起到湖南视察。一天他们同乘一辆轿车，行至湘江橘子洲头岸边，毛泽东追忆青年时代在这里读书和从事革命活动的情景，不由豪兴勃发，提出和周恩来对对子助兴。毛泽东即景咏出上联。周恩来正在思索时，小车驶到当年毛泽东常和同学们谈论天下大事的天心阁。这时，一群鸽子从阁内飞出。周恩来灵机一动，忙说：“主席，对子的下联我对出来了。”接着念出了下联，毛泽东会心地微笑着。"}],"contents":[{"id":"f884e656c9","type":"title","text":"和周恩来应对联！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"5d431ea32d"},{"id":"7ace84c88d","type":"paragraph","text":"橘子洲，洲旁舟，舟行洲不行：（毛泽东天心阁，阁中鸽，鸽飞阁不飞。（周恩来）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"5d431ea32d"}],"page":{"id":"4299b33da8","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"5d431ea32d","start":209,"end":209}}}},"__N_SSG":true}